metadata.name: Mannequins
metadata.description:
Ominous Season One.

Episode One: Mannequins.

"Attention, attention, this is an emergency broadcast. A mysterious light has been spotted in the sky and is rapidly spreading across the city. We urge you to avoid looking at the light at all costs.

It has been reported that those who have looked directly at the light have experienced, blindness, hearing loss, hardened skin and Full Body Paralysis. We are unsure of the origin or purpose of the light, but we advise all citizens to stay indoors and avoid looking outside.

If you must leave your home, use caution and stay in areas with low light levels. Avoid open spaces and do not look directly at the light. We repeat, do not look directly at the light.

We are currently working to determine the cause of the light and how to protect citizens from its effects. In the meantime, please stay calm and follow all safety protocols.

Again, this is an emergency broadcast warning of a mysterious and anomalous light that you should avoid at all costs. Stay safe and stay indoors."
